snippet.title: Paranormal Investigators - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Paranormal Investigators is a 4 player co-op horror. You and your team are the hosts of a local TV show and explore abandoned houses with paranormal activity. You must make a video report and survive until dawn.

👻Add to wishlist on Steam👻
